          },
          "endTime": {
            "value": "10:00"
          },
          "notes": "Whimsical pink-upholstered café. Breakfast in the Gallery room. Booking essential — one of London's most Instagrammed interiors."
        },
        {
          "location": {
            "searchKey": "Selfridges, Oxford Street, London",
