          },
          "endTime": {
            "value": "13:00"
          },
          "notes": "Europe's busiest shopping street. Selfridges is the anchor — hit the beauty hall and food hall. Also check John Lewis and Marks & Spencer."
        },
        {
          "location": {
            "searchKey": "Carnaby Street, London",
            "lat": 51.5128,
            "lon": -0.1397
          },
          "day": 2,
          "startTime": {
            "value": "13:00"
          },
          "endTime": {
            "value": "14:00"
          },
          "notes": "Pedestrianised street lined with cafés. Good for a relaxed sit-down lunch — try Kua 'Aina for burgers or Flatbread Kitchen for mezze."
        },
        {
          "location": {
            "searchKey": "Liberty London, Great Marlborough Street",
            "lat": 51.5132,
            "lon": -0.1407
